{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/eb8818430765fce04e96ac3c59e740635a1b6880/comments/5643343.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/eb8818430765fce04e96ac3c59e740635a1b6880?path=cmake%2FFindOGRE.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/eb8818430765fce04e96ac3c59e740635a1b6880#comment-5643343"}}, "deleted": false, "commit": {"hash": "eb8818430765fce04e96ac3c59e740635a1b6880", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/eb8818430765fce04e96ac3c59e740635a1b6880.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/eb8818430765fce04e96ac3c59e740635a1b6880"}}}, "content": {"raw": "If you want to allow users to be able to specify `OPTIONAL_COMPONENTS` in their call to `find_package(~)`, you can change this line to \n\n```\nelseif(OGRE_FIND_REQUIRED_${component})\n```\n\nThat way, if `${component}` was listed under `OPTIONAL_COMPONENTS` instead of `COMPONENTS`, it will not set `OGRE_FOUND` to `false`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>If you want to allow users to be able to specify <code>OPTIONAL_COMPONENTS</code> in their call to <code>find_package(~)</code>, you can change this line to </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>elseif(OGRE_FIND_REQUIRED_<span class=\"cp\">${</span><span class=\"n\">component</span><span class=\"cp\">}</span>)\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>That way, if <code>${component}</code> was listed under <code>OPTIONAL_COMPONENTS</code> instead of <code>COMPONENTS</code>, it will not set <code>OGRE_FOUND</code> to <code>false</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-01-06T00:34:40.406242+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdf